# Browsers that we support

# Production browsers
# Target modern browsers that support ES2022 features natively
> 0.2%
not dead
not op_mini all

# Modern Chrome (supports all ES2022 features)
Chrome >= 91

# Modern Firefox (supports all ES2022 features)
Firefox >= 90

# Modern Safari (supports most ES2022 features)
Safari >= 14

# Modern Edge (Chromium-based)
Edge >= 91

# Exclude very old browsers that would require heavy polyfills
not IE 11
not Chrome < 91
not Firefox < 90
not Safari < 14
not Edge < 91

# Mobile browsers
iOS >= 14
Android >= 91
